"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Are you a New Yorker doing something amazing and could use $200,000 to support your work?\\n\\nIf so, you should apply for a David Prize. I have written about this program before so you might remember. But for those who haven’t heard about it, here’s the deal:\\n\\n![](https://avc.com/content/uploads/2021/11/Screen-Shot-2020-10-27-at-6.09.45-AM.png)\\n\\nHere are the most recent cohort of [David Prize winners](http://thedavidprize.org/winners/):\\n\\n●     **Cesar Vargas**: Fighting for immigrants in the armed forces and their right to stay in the U.S.\\n\\n●     **Fela Barclift**: Sparking academic excellence and positive self-esteem among NYC’s youngest learners ([this video](https://www.usatoday.com/videos/news/nation/2021/10/20/nyc-african-heritage-preschool-founder-wins-prize/6107220001/) is amazing)\\n\\n●     **Felicia Wilson:** Inspiring foster care alumni to support young people “aging out”\\n\\n●     **Mr. Five Mualimm-ak**: Creating essential community for justice-impacted youth serving supervision sentences\\n\\n●     **Jaime-Jin Lewis**: Envisioning a childcare system where providers, families, and children can thrive\\n\\nThe folks behind the David Prize are looking for broader representation from the “the tech / science / invention circles” which describes many AVC readers.\\n\\nIf you want to apply for a David Prize, you can do so [here](https://thedavidprize.submittable.com/submit). Applications are due by December 21st.\\n\",\"timestamp\":1637146276,\"title\":\"The David Prize - AVC\",\"publication\":\"avc\"},\"digest\":\"IIZ1DmqYmeNHznr7npzsakBQ7XA9wbYJUDwISI0-sH4\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xB8332710AB60A1B2e8FE6D775d83524C9E0cE136\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"7KeePGIAs00v-N4vKlrUaTL5OeOcqObJn-Nplbq8QD8\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"RaWR8QS-wmtpDa9uyXF30DVeV831cOs7H7C8SzuDYqI\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"ZsfDNsmZLIvYwxPTlfb-Qyk